sentence: show me all first class fares from new york to miami leaving on a tuesday
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v1.class_type||'"',
 '"'||v2.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v3.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v3.day_name||'"', '"'||v4.fare_id||'"', '"'||v5.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v6.airport_code||'"', '"'||v7.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.city_name||'"', '"'||v8.airport_code||'"', '"'||v9.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v9.city_name||'"', '"'||v10.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v10.day_name||'"' FROM fare v0, fare_basis v1,
 fare_basis v2, days v3, flight_fare v4, flight v5, airport_service v6,
 city v7, airport_service v8, city v9, days v10 
WHERE (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v1.fare_basis_code) AND (v1.class_type = 'FIRST')) 
AND (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v2.fare_basis_code) 
AND ((v2.basis_days = ANY v3.days_code) AND (v3.day_name = 'TUESDAY'))) 
AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v4.fare_id) 
AND ((v4.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) AND (((v5.from_airport = ANY v6.airport_code) 
AND ((v6.city_code = ANY v7.city_code) 
AND (v7.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) AND (((v5.to_airport = ANY v8.airport_code) 
AND ((v8.city_code = ANY v9.city_code) 
AND (v9.city_name = 'MIAMI'))) AND ((v5.flight_days = ANY v10.days_code) 
AND (v10.day_name = 'TUESDAY'))))))));

FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' TUESDAY ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
